Final Layer Normalization
│
├── 1. Input Hidden State
│     ├── Tensor shape: (batch_size × seq_len × hidden_dim)
│     └── Output from final transformer decoder layer
│
├── 2. Mean Computation
│     ├── Compute mean across hidden dimension
│     └── μ = (1 / hidden_dim) Σ x_i
│
├── 3. Variance Computation
│     ├── Compute variance across hidden dimension
│     └── σ² = (1 / hidden_dim) Σ (x_i − μ)²
│
├── 4. Numerical Stability Adjustment
│     └── Add epsilon (ε) to variance
│
├── 5. Standard Deviation
│     └── sqrt(σ² + ε)
│
├── 6. Normalization
│     └── (x − μ) / sqrt(σ² + ε)
│
├── 7. Scale Transformation
│     ├── Multiply by learnable parameter γ
│     └── γ shape: (hidden_dim)
│
├── 8. Bias Transformation
│     ├── Add learnable parameter β
│     └── β shape: (hidden_dim)
│
├── 9. Output Hidden State
│     └── Passed to Output Projection Layer (LM Head)